===============================================================================
    log4php
===============================================================================

Summary

    Log4php is a php port of the most popular java logging framework log4j 
    (see http://jakarta.apache.org/log4j/ for details).

Installation

    See INSTALL file.
    
Documentation

    . Main documentation in docs/
    
    . API documentation in docs/api
    
    . Log4j documentation at 
        http://jakarta.apache.org/log4j/docs/documentation.html
    
Credits

    Framework design, strategies and part of the methods documention are 
    developed by log4j team (2)(3) (Ceki Gülcü as log4j project founder and 
    contributors).

    PHP port, extensions and modifications by VxR (1). All rights reserved.
    For more information, please see log4php homepage (1).

